title: arm32: Build fails with error: #error "TARGET_RUST_OS_INFO already defined in bpabi.h
body:
Trying to build revision ff4715d79e2c17d270db8b94315aa6b574f48994 on arm32 fails with:

```
g++ -c   -g -O2 -DIN_GCC     -fno-exceptions -fno-rtti -fasynchronous-unwind-tables -W -Wall -Wno-narrowing -Wwrite-strings -Wcast-qual -Wno-error=format-diag -Wmissing-format-attribute -Woverloaded-virtual -pedantic -Wno-long-long -Wno-variadic-macros -Wno-overlength-strings -fno-common  -DHAVE_CONFIG_H  -DGENERATOR_FILE -fno-PIE -I. -Ibuild -I../../gcc -I../../gcc/build -I../../gcc/../include  -I../../gcc/../libcpp/include  \
        -o build/rtl.o ../../gcc/rtl.c
In file included from ./tm.h:35,
                 from ../../gcc/genpreds.c:26:
../../gcc/config/arm/bpabi.h:113:3: error: #error "TARGET_RUST_OS_INFO already defined in bpabi.h - c++ undefines it and redefines it."
  113 | # error "TARGET_RUST_OS_INFO already defined in bpabi.h - c++ undefines it and redefines it."
      |   ^~~~~
../../gcc/config/arm/bpabi.h:115: warning: "TARGET_RUST_OS_INFO" redefined
  115 | #define TARGET_RUST_OS_INFO() \
      |
In file included from ./tm.h:34,
                 from ../../gcc/genpreds.c:26:
../../gcc/config/arm/linux-elf.h:86: note: this is the location of the previous definition
   86 | #define TARGET_RUST_OS_INFO()  \
      |
In file included from ./tm.h:35,
                 from ../../gcc/rtl.c:30:
../../gcc/config/arm/bpabi.h:113:3: error: #error "TARGET_RUST_OS_INFO already defined in bpabi.h - c++ undefines it and redefines it."
  113 | # error "TARGET_RUST_OS_INFO already defined in bpabi.h - c++ undefines it and redefines it."
      |   ^~~~~
../../gcc/config/arm/bpabi.h:115: warning: "TARGET_RUST_OS_INFO" redefined
  115 | #define TARGET_RUST_OS_INFO() \
      |
In file included from ./tm.h:34,
                 from ../../gcc/rtl.c:30:
../../gcc/config/arm/linux-elf.h:86: note: this is the location of the previous definition
   86 | #define TARGET_RUST_OS_INFO()  \
      |
```
